# dev 镜像构建：尽量缩小 context，减轻 Mac Docker VM 压力
.git
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
*.egg-info
build/
dist/
csrc/build/
csrc/build_out/
csrc/output/
vllm_ascend/_cann_ops_custom/
offline-a3-bundle/images/
vllm-ascend-a3-offline-*.tar.gz
*.tar.gz
!offline-a3-bundle/sources/*.tar.gz
# 与 dev 镜像无关的大目录
tests/
docs/
benchmarks/
examples/
.github/
.agents/
*.md
!tools/offline-a3-dev/README.md
